item.title: #185 - William Wickline
item.description: William’s childhood appeared normal and uneventful until around the age of 17, when things began to take a darker turn and he started accumulating a criminal record. As an adult his behavior spiraled further, leading him into a life of serious crimes. For years, he managed to evade justice despite being involved in increasingly heinous acts. Was his descent into violence triggered by an alleged drug debt, or was it simply the inevitable outcome of the path he had chosen? . . . This week we di...
